Alex Giannini https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alex_Giannini 0 Alex Giannini (born Alexander von Giannini; 6 June 1958 – 2 October 2015) was an English actor on stage, television and film. His work included comedy and musicals as well as drama. Alex_Giannini ( born Alexander_von_Giannini ; 6_June_1958 – 2_October_2015 ) was an_English_actor on stage_,_television_and_film .
